Prerequisites:
  ruby: 1.9
  gems: unicode_utils
  apt: texlive-latex-base, texlive-latex-extra

Example to stdout:
  PATH_TO/badge -f FIRSTNAME -s SECONDNAME -l LASTNAME -c COMPANYNAME -a CATEGORY -q PATH_TO/qrCode.png | lpr

Example to file:
  PATH_TO/badge -f FIRSTNAME -s SECONDNAME -l LASTNAME -c COMPANYNAME -a CATEGORY -q PATH_TO/qrCode.png -o badge.pdf

Example two days:
  PATH_TO/badge -f FIRSTNAME -s SECONDNAME -l LASTNAME -c COMPANYNAME -a CATEGORY -q PATH_TO/qrCode.png -2 | lpr

Example two days and VIP:
  PATH_TO/badge -f FIRSTNAME -s SECONDNAME -l LASTNAME -c COMPANYNAME -a CATEGORY -q PATH_TO/qrCode.png -2 -i | lpr

Example debug:

  PATH_TO/badge -d -f FIRSTNAME -s SECONDNAME -l LASTNAME -c COMPANYNAME -a CATEGORY -2 -q PATH_TO/qrCode.png

Help: 

  PATH_TO/badge -h

